-- American States Water Agrees to Acquire California’s Rural Water
-- B y   J u s t i n   D o o m
-- 2013-06-13T19:50:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-13/american-states-water-agrees-to-acquire-california-s-rural-water.html
American States Water Co., a
California-based water and power provider, agreed to buy Rural
Water Co.  Rural Water Co. serves about 940 customers in Arroyo
Grande, California, in San Luis Obispo County, according to a
filing today.  Terms of the purchase by American’s Golden State Water unit
weren’t disclosed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Doom in  New York  at 
 jdoom1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Randall Hackley at 
 rhackley@bloomberg.net  